      "rationale": "Manufacturer-supplied benchmark verification cases (lid-driven cavity, Poiseuille flow, rotating disk) confirm correct implementation of the Navier-Stokes solver and turbulence model. Results match published analytical and numerical reference solutions within expected numerical tolerances."
