      "rationale": "Validation was performed using the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, which shares key geometric features (impeller diameter, volute design, clearance gaps) with the subject CPB device. Operating conditions span the clinical CPB flow range. The validation domain is judged sufficiently similar to the COU for MRL 2 purposes."
