    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for the CFD hemolysis prediction model has been reviewed across all 13 ASME V&V 40 factors. Seven factors were formally assessed and all achieved their required credibility levels or above. Six factors were appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The model demonstrates sufficient credibility for the intended COU: identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied at all five evaluated operating points. The assessment team unanimously accepts the simulation results as credible evidence in support of the regulatory submission.",
